## Backend env vars (DO NOT commit real secrets)

# Required for AI explanation:
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-your-key-here

# Optional:
DEEPSEEK_BASE_URL=https://api.deepseek.com
DEEPSEEK_MODEL=deepseek-chat

# CORS origins, comma-separated (set to your GitHub Pages origin)
# Example:
# CORS_ALLOW_ORIGINS=https://<username>.github.io,http://127.0.0.1:8010

